1. *Sistemu* je potrebno unapređenje. (The *system* needs improvement.)
2. Izveštaji pokazuju da *sistem* nije efikasan. (Reports show that the *system* is not efficient.)
3. Radimo na integraciji novih softverskih *sistema*. (We are working on integrating new software *systems*.)
4. *Sistem* zaštite podataka je veoma važan za bezbednost. (The data protection *system* is very important for security.)
5. Nismo sigurni da li *sistem* funkcioniše ispravno. (We are not sure if the *system* is working properly.)
6. Pokrećemo novi *sistem* za upravljanje zalihama. (We are launching a new *system* for inventory management.)
7. Potrebno je da se *sistem* redovno održava kako bi se izbegle greške. (It is necessary to regularly maintain the *system* in order to avoid errors.)
8. Ova organizacija ima vrlo dobro uspostavljen *sistem* upravljanja kvalitetom. (This organization has a very well-established quality management *system*.)
9. Prilikom instaliranja novog *sistema* došlo je do nekih komplikacija. (There were some complications during the installation of the new *system*.)
10. *Sistem* koji smo koristili do sada nije bio dovoljno pouzdan. (The *system* we have been using so far has not been reliable enough.)